{"tid":128391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以叫男朋友唔好咁大洗⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-02-20T18:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:11:22.000Z","uid":4998,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66e03e56f27164b4f9e0afe66254abadfa83ad88","tid":128391,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:35:50.000Z","msg":"男朋友差人成萬卡數 因為賭輸左 實際數字唔太清楚<br />\n平時份人又好大洗  成日買衫買褲買鞋<br />\n成日佢話戎賭 呢排話戎架啦戎架啦 <br />\n轉個頭又賭返 然後輸錢 無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時佢都有返工既 但搵埋都唔夠洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我地未到談婚論嫁既地步<br />\n但都想佢腳踏實地少少"},{"pid":"21f529c18d8f53fe7bb6cea9c4c104c05f7c32ec","tid":128391,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:38:01.000Z","msg":"有無絲打分享下經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我都唔知可以點做⋯⋯"},{"pid":"c7408de7fae04e453024f28bbd80a64245573713","tid":128391,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:38:18.000Z","msg":"賭仔死撚硬<br />\n輸錢唔識停既賭仔更加死得快<br />\n快d 止蝕"},{"pid":"9864ffee41522972fad3be146b7f886816ab120b","tid":128391,"uid":18980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:38:50.000Z","msg":"等佢賴次大既就自己會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你愛佢就陪住佢 等佢知佢仲有你 <br />\n你覺得你唔夠愛既就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb32b731771a127b20c6f8e0c88a7fb9a0879ccd","tid":128391,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:39:05.000Z","msg":"一萬數做一個月都有<br />\n但會賭錢就..."},{"pid":"53866a1e5eda237114d1864fe1e7dabc36212bb2","tid":128391,"uid":82396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:39:13.000Z","msg":"飛咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed75abcaa8c0ac4ff63c27d4155581b3cdf9a358","tid":128391,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:39:18.000Z","msg":"利申：賭仔，暪住條女出去賭，但個個月嬴幾萬<br />\n所以賭博唔係問題，輸錢又大洗先係問題"},{"pid":"a5b7aad91e15afc3489752fc1b686721aac19809","tid":128391,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等佢賴次大既就自己會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你愛佢就陪住佢 等佢知佢仲有你 <br />\n你覺得你唔夠愛既就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好愛佢<br />\n佢對我好好 <br />\n但係我真係唔想佢再賭落去同咁大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a33b887bc8a2eea81b452208aa8a230eb4d6f8a","tid":128391,"uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"幾個賭錢賭到家破人亡，幾層樓都可以照輸哂<br />\n總之輸錢唔識停既賭仔，勸唔停既就要止蝕啦"},{"pid":"5f4a12288c64796d8437c0399698404e1eabfb1d","tid":128391,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:45:09.000Z","msg":"咁年輕就賭唔停，點得到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我讀u試過賭1千蚊1注，一晚輸晒一個月pt糧<br />\n之後勁心痛即戒賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果戒極都戒唔到，係有病要打戒賭熱線啦"},{"pid":"bde52e78cfa1eabac7655b4793f758b2535b9d44","tid":128391,"uid":28481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80qVs24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80qVs24.jpg&h=f99252c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00f2a54550e0dccf396054a079e31cceda0772a2","tid":128391,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁年輕就賭唔停，點得到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我讀u試過賭1千蚊1注，一晚輸晒一個月pt糧<br />\n之後勁心痛即戒賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果戒極都戒唔到，係有病要打戒賭熱線啦</blockquote><br />\n一千蚊一注都心痛真係唔應該賭"},{"pid":"ee4c4fdf69774ffb2b9d55e884c050596b1c93d1","tid":128391,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:46:48.000Z","msg":"朝朝幫佢出野<br />\n省返叫雞錢"},{"pid":"e9ee8f5a93978294184d713c9129bb5cbba81b31","tid":128391,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:48:18.000Z","msg":"賭仔唔賭就唔會叫賭仔啦"},{"pid":"d672894c367aefcf2867107c8d98dc96c962f3e0","tid":128391,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:48:27.000Z","msg":"分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af44f976aed53e06fc80895c2fb39c06a435973","tid":128391,"uid":18980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等佢賴次大既就自己會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你愛佢就陪住佢 等佢知佢仲有你 <br />\n你覺得你唔夠愛既就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好愛佢<br />\n佢對我好好 <br />\n但係我真係唔想佢再賭落去同咁大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賭既心態真係唔賭既人諗唔明(雖然我都唔賭)<br />\n你愈㩒住佢 佢就愈大心癮去賭 你限制佢財政咩? 佢出面借返黎都會拎去賭<br />\n你唯有勸佢慢慢去戒<br />\n我見得多 自己都經歷緊 你唯一做既就係等佢明等佢識諗<br />\n等到你心灰意冷佢都仲未明 咪就係走既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你叫佢即時斷唔賭其實真係好撚難 戒一樣野唔係話唔睇就唔睇 你有野上癮既時候一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下戒開lihkg個app 你就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adebfd1d9e67acd1da76f3d0468a5a5f88cf32e7","tid":128391,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁年輕就賭唔停，點得到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我讀u試過賭1千蚊1注，一晚輸晒一個月pt糧<br />\n之後勁心痛即戒賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果戒極都戒唔到，係有病要打戒賭熱線啦</blockquote><br />\n一千蚊一注都心痛真係唔應該賭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚讀緊書身無分文，又唔會問老母攞錢，輸緊嘅係做pt搵返來嘅食飯搭車錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一次就驚左，注定我做唔到賭仔"},{"pid":"13a76f779c4cea9b01a686b06ab8edde9eb12cde","tid":128391,"uid":18980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁年輕就賭唔停，點得到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我讀u試過賭1千蚊1注，一晚輸晒一個月pt糧<br />\n之後勁心痛即戒賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果戒極都戒唔到，係有病要打戒賭熱線啦</blockquote><br />\n一千蚊一注都心痛真係唔應該賭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚讀緊書身無分文，又唔會問老母攞錢，輸緊嘅係做pt搵返來嘅食飯搭車錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一次就驚左，注定我做唔到賭仔</blockquote><br />\n好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986dd3ba62df375335ac667c40c1f83e747d9a44","tid":128391,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等佢賴次大既就自己會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你愛佢就陪住佢 等佢知佢仲有你 <br />\n你覺得你唔夠愛既就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好愛佢<br />\n佢對我好好 <br />\n但係我真係唔想佢再賭落去同咁大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賭既心態真係唔賭既人諗唔明(雖然我都唔賭)<br />\n你愈㩒住佢 佢就愈大心癮去賭 你限制佢財政咩? 佢出面借返黎都會拎去賭<br />\n你唯有勸佢慢慢去戒<br />\n我見得多 自己都經歷緊 你唯一做既就係等佢明等佢識諗<br />\n等到你心灰意冷佢都仲未明 咪就係走既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你叫佢即時斷唔賭其實真係好撚難 戒一樣野唔係話唔睇就唔睇 你有野上癮既時候一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下戒開lihkg個app 你就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 多謝你<br />\n你都面臨緊同樣既問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f07b105121ab905320b18ab55636164639d96c","tid":128391,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"得幾個%既賭仔可以長期贏錢<br />\n<br />\n冇本冇經驗冇人教  輸死未天光"},{"pid":"98235ec15af2459eb5d5996ad9d92996db0ed74f","tid":128391,"uid":18980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等佢賴次大既就自己會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你愛佢就陪住佢 等佢知佢仲有你 <br />\n你覺得你唔夠愛既就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好愛佢<br />\n佢對我好好 <br />\n但係我真係唔想佢再賭落去同咁大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賭既心態真係唔賭既人諗唔明(雖然我都唔賭)<br />\n你愈㩒住佢 佢就愈大心癮去賭 你限制佢財政咩? 佢出面借返黎都會拎去賭<br />\n你唯有勸佢慢慢去戒<br />\n我見得多 自己都經歷緊 你唯一做既就係等佢明等佢識諗<br />\n等到你心灰意冷佢都仲未明 咪就係走既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你叫佢即時斷唔賭其實真係好撚難 戒一樣野唔係話唔睇就唔睇 你有野上癮既時候一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下戒開lihkg個app 你就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 多謝你<br />\n你都面臨緊同樣既問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題上係我未識佢之前績落既大過你 你個個都係細數黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就前幾個月 我日日都話佢哦佢 係咁逼佢唔好賭<br />\n咁你應該都明結果係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家傾過 佢會戒但真係要慢慢黎<br />\n其實我諗諗下 又真係 你要我即戒一樣野我都唔得<br />\n咪每個月set個limit囉 大家都可以接受既範圍咁<br />\n<br />\n溝通好重要 而家嗌交都少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283fa5306b711430080f51377a109cbb31b5630a","tid":128391,"uid":52474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:19:20.000Z","msg":"條仔死性不改，咁都仲唔飛佢，搏佢有一日會改，睇黎你先係超級賭徒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賭注係自己既青春，甚至一生，值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n利申：阿媽賭輸左一生畀個仆街老豆"},{"pid":"50e024c138f788d200e52a2b3b2ec5c27a0f4395","tid":128391,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條仔死性不改，咁都仲唔飛佢，搏佢有一日會改，睇黎你先係超級賭徒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賭注係自己既青春，甚至一生，值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n利申：阿媽賭輸左一生畀個仆街老豆</blockquote><br />\n賭真係幾多錢幾多愛都唔夠<br />\n建議樓主快d搵過件仲好，雖然你唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ebaa686fdd6f75b23b63d35813f034a5710273","tid":128391,"uid":50202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:58:24.000Z","msg":"戎你老母"},{"pid":"92c4e86983c1d809ac77316a0ae62ac2cd1a7217","tid":128391,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:06:47.000Z","msg":"仆街 你係咪我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d4ada2005d23783f66580cd5d5ce2492d41317","tid":128391,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T21:33:44.000Z","msg":"繼續同佢一齊, 結埋婚, 賭到冇家用, 有樓變冇樓, 日日打老婆打仔, 借錢借到斷六親, 大耳窿上門追數, 個仔大咗有樣學樣... <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d0713b5945c16066bc14e5c7bf2437420e5828","tid":128391,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T22:24:06.000Z","msg":"飛撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"9ddbc5ac27e0234965f7882165339d6973a4043f","tid":128391,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條仔死性不改，咁都仲唔飛佢，搏佢有一日會改，睇黎你先係超級賭徒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賭注係自己既青春，甚至一生，值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n利申：阿媽賭輸左一生畀個仆街老豆</blockquote><br />\n咁佢除左賭錢同大洗呢樣野之外<br />\n其他方面真係對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢既每一樣回憶<br />\n唔係話分就分到架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人無完美係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時諗就算識過個唔賭既<br />\n可能佢 都會有其他缺點<br />\n例如花心周圍搞女點點點<br />\n咪仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad271157a3206b71b4971262c9796949cc