到d咩<br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人"},{"pid":"72e763049125654ba4fe82dc337840896993561d","tid":128391,"uid":5733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等佢賴次大既就自己會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你愛佢就陪住佢 等佢知佢仲有你 <br />\n你覺得你唔夠愛既就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好愛佢<br />\n佢對我好好 <br />\n但係我真係唔想佢再賭落去同咁大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好條撚啊，你幾時病聽過賭仔會對人好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家條友未輸到走投無路炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛得啦"},{"pid":"0506768351ceab65ede41293005b09f30c6515c1","tid":128391,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"衰大洗可以改 衰賭真係好難攪 好自為之"},{"pid":"f748aa6c6d78999b846b8a989ff29f377040a855","tid":128391,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續同佢一齊, 結埋婚, 賭到冇家用, 有樓變冇樓, 日日打老婆打仔, 借錢借到斷六親, 大耳窿上門追數, 個仔大咗有樣學樣... <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個仔未必既，自己老豆賭唔停，由細被人追數追到慣<br />\n我由懂事開始已經好憎賭錢，六合彩都唔願買<br />\n連玩8pool $500 一場都覺得好大壓力唔想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但<br />\n賭仔要改都唔易，改唔到就走啦<br />\n無必要同佢賭埋自己。"},{"pid":"2a1fe308d1a9aeeae08bf6a6ddac202023d1082d","tid":128391,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04b1025937fcbe3f3385b11722850ad339af8f7c","tid":128391,"uid":24025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b8a67eba43cc23023f46e9dfe074744db6fe69f","tid":128391,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:19:01.000Z","ms